With over 5000 sales professionals in more than 75 sales offices across the Tri-State area, the company was recently acknowledged as #1, for the seventh year in a row, in the entire national Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Network. Through its affiliated services, the Trident Group and Prosperity Home Mortgage, LLC; the company provides one-stop shopping and facilitated services to its clients including mortgage financing, and title, property and casualty insurance. The company-sponsored charitable foundation, Fox & Roach/Trident Charities, is committed to addressing the needs of children and families in stressful life circumstances and has contributed over $8 million to more than 250 local organizations since its inception in 1995. Visit us at www.foxroach.com

data.description: NEW PRICE!  Incredible value for this beautiful home offering at Gateway North in Parkland SD. This very special home boasts a first floor master suite, walk-in closet with custom built-ins. Master bath features dual vanity, over-sized whirlpool tub private water closet, tile floors and separate shower. You will fall in love with this very, special home from the moment you walk in the door. Open concept floor plan focuses on the center family room with soaring vaulted ceilings showcasing the second story catwalk style balcony. 3 more generous sized bedrooms and a large bonus perfect for an office/den or hobby room complete the second level. Hardwood floors throughout first level, formal dining room with Butler's pantry. Kitchen is complete with stainless appliances and wrap-around bar Peninsula. Vaulted ceilings are showcased in Breakfast Room. Beautifully finished Family Room in lower level adds an additional 875 SF of living space. Deck w/ Paver patio, professionally landscaped w/ outdoor lighting. Interior of home was just freshly painted and NEW wall to wall carpeting installed. 2023-10-17
